description:
Zero Two is an elite pilot with the pseudonym "The Partner Killer", given the mysterious happening of her co-pilots dying after a short number of Franxx outings. Her Franxx partner is http://anidb.net/ch92216 [Hiro]. She is very fond of sweet taste and her personality is described as dangerous yet alluring.
Source: Darling in the Franxx Wiki
name: Zero Two
